Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:11.88,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{My little brother Kamil is so adorable!}Em trai Kamil của tớ dễ thương lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.19,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{He was just born, so he's so tiny,}Vừa sinh ra nên nhỏ xíu à.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.70,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{and whenever he cries, he \Ngets so red and wrinkly.}Mỗi khi khóc thằng bé đều đỏ hỏn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.65,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I never knew a little \Nbrother could be so cute.}Không ngờ em trai cháu lại dễ thương vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:25.22,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{That's enough.}Đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.13,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{I get enough of doting parents \Nfrom being around Otto.}Chú nghe mấy câu đó từ Otto hoài.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:31.84,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{What?! Missus. Corinna had her baby, then?}Hả? Tiểu thư Corina cũng sinh rồi ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:35.95,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{At the end of winter.\N Her name is Renate.}Vào cuối mùa đông, con bé tên Renate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:40.71,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{She'll be the Gilberta Company's heiress.\N I hope you'll look after her.}Con bé sẽ thừa kế thương hội này nên nhờ cháu cả đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:46.10,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{You don't seem that excited, considering \Nshe's your precious heiress.}Trông chú có vẻ không hứng khởi nhỉ. Là người thừa kế đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:50.56,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{Yes, because Otto is excited \Nenough for the both of us.}À, Otto thay chú hứng khởi mỗi ngày rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.56,Default,Otto,0,0,0,,{Renate's absolutely adorable, \Nno matter what she does.}Renate làm gì cũng dễ thương cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.95,Default,Otto,0,0,0,,{Renate's absolutely adorable, \Nno matter what she does.}Renate làm gì cũng dễ thương cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:02.07,Default,Corinna,0,0,0,,{Stop playing with your food, dear.}Đừng có chơi với đồ ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:06.32,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Thank goodness the Gilberta \NCompany has Missus. Corinna.}Thật may khi thương hội Gilberta có cô Corinna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:09.43,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{More importantly, hurry up and \Ntell me about the printing.}Quan trọng hơn là bàn về vụ in ấn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.15,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:15.53,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{The head priest has told me not to do \Nany letterpress printing for a while.}Linh mục trưởng nói cháu tạm thời không phát triển máy in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:22.43,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{If we keep moving forward, the vested \Ninterest opposing us will be the nobility.}Nếu cứ tiếp tục sẽ ảnh hưởng đến một vài quý tộc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:25.36,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{A vested interest of nobles...}Một vài quý tộc à...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:28.92,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{Discretion is the better \Npart of valor indeed.}Thận trọng là tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:34.32,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{So I want to put everything into \Nmaking picture books for a while.}Thế nên cháu sẽ tập trung vào làm sách tranh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:38.77,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{Everything? What are you plotting?}Tập trung hoàn toàn? Cháu định làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:43.37,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{First, I want to create some colored ink \Nso we can add colors to the pictures.}Đầu tiên cháu muốn tạo mực màu để tô màu cho tranh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:47.08,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Second, improving our mimeograph technology.}Thứ hai là cải tiến công nghệ của chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:51.78,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{Colored ink and improving \Nmimeograph technology?}Mực màu và cải tiến nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:55.28,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Yes, but we'll have to hurry and \Nprepare, or we won't make it in time.}Vâng, cần phải nhanh chuẩn bị nếu không sẽ không kịp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.00,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{In time? For what?}Không kịp gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:03.05,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Why, creating a picture book to go \Nalong with my precious Kamil's growth.}Dĩ nhiên là phải làm xong nó trước khi Kamil lớn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.85,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{I'm going to give this \Nmy all for Kamil's sake!}Cháu sẽ cố gắng hết sức vì Kamil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.84,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{Did you get permission from the head priest?}Đã được linh mục trưởng cho phép chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.23,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{If you did, that's fine.}Nếu rồi thì không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:14.43,Default,Benno,0,0,0,,{I'll let you meet the foreman \Nof the workshop soon.}Chú sẽ dẫn cháu đi gặp trưởng xưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.74,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{Thank you kindly.}Cảm ơn chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:23.51,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{My little brother was born the other day.}Em trai tớ vừa sinh đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:25.27,Default,Gil and Rosina,0,0,0,,{Congratulations.}Chúc mừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:30.03,Default,Delia,0,0,0,,{Oh, I had no idea.}Chẳng biết gì luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:34.03,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{Oh, no. I was so excited that I let\N the cat out of the bag myself.}Chết, mình vui quá nên lỡ mồm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:36.87,Default,Gil,0,0,0,,{Lady Main, what's your brother's name?}Tên em ấy là gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.84,Italics,Main,0,0,0,,{Nice follow up, Gil! Yay!}Hay lắm Gil!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.84,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{His name is Kamil.}Tên nó là Kamil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:44.42,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{He was just born, so he's really tiny.}Vừa sinh nên nhỏ xíu à.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.74,Default,Main,0,0,0,,{And when he cries, he gets \Nall red and wrinkly.}Mỗi khi khóc mặt đỏ lên.
